title: Mozart - The Wind Concertos - Orpheus CO
description:
Mozart: The Wind Concertos.

Disc I
Sinfonia Concertante for Oboe, Clarinet, Horn, Bassoon and Orchestra, Clarinet Concerto, Andante for Flute and Orchestra.

Disc II
Bassoon Concerto, Horn Concertos, 1 - 4.

Disc III
Oboe Concerto, Flute Concerto, Flute & Harp Concerto.

I remember collecting these wonderful CDs separately as they were published in the late 1980s. This three disc collection was released by DG in 2002.

Please enjoy.
